title: Ocean View Single Family Home 745 Taylor, Crescent City,
text:
Ocean View Single Family Home 745 Taylor, Crescent City, ad date: 10/24/2015 
Single Family Home 745 Taylor, Crescent City, CA 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, 2,458 sq. ft. home on .30 acres. Attached 3-car garage, fireplace and heat pump. Close to Joe Hamilton Elementary and Crescent Elk Middle Schools and 1.1 mile from Del Norte High. Just one block from the ocean! MLS 1500453 $385,000 Jim Nelson, Agent 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Office: 707-465-2121 Cell: 707-218-7240
